Important commands:

  mkwiz <name>                : promote a player to wizard
  mkwizdir <name>             : create a wizard directory
  mkadmin <name>              : promote a player to admin
  rmuser <name>               : remove the named player (and force it offline)
  shutdown <delay> <reason>   : shutdown the mud
  warmboot                    : recompile everything

Important documentation:

  General information manpages:

    history

  Configuration:

    local_config, driver_config
    
  The following manpages contain important information about coding for 
  Gurbalib:

    objects, rebuild, security, kfun, afun

  
